B.aec=new A.lH("How I Talked to My Kids About Cancer (At Ages 5 and 8)","Sarah J.","SJ","Breast Cancer","5 min read","My daughter thought cancer was contagious. My son thought I was going to die. Getting this conversation right was the hardest thing I've ever done \u2014 and some of what worked might surprise you...",B.qG,B.Tf,4500)
B.V5=s(["Gratitude","Survivorship","Life Lessons"],t.s)
B.aed=new A.lH("Finding Gratitude in the Worst Year of My Life","Lisa T.","LT","Lymphoma","7 min read",'I know "cancer was a gift" is a clich\xe9 that many find offensive \u2014 and I get that. But for me, facing mortality reshuffled everything I thought mattered. Here is what actually changed...',B.C,B.V5,3200)
